  "body": "<a href=\"https://marvvinekk.crevado.com/work-collection\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w8eEzFr.png\" title=\"AUTHOR\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\"/>\n</a>\n<br></br>\n<center>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/marvvinekk/projects\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jKNqMhu.png\" title=\"CURSEFORGE\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"/>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Marvvinekk\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wcQ70ci.png\" title=\"MODRINTH\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"/>\n    </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Marvvinekk\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LF4oCPW.png\" title=\"DISCORD\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"/>\n    </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Marvvinekk\">\n        <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PCBmCD0.png\" title=\"KOFI\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"150\" height=\"50\"/>\n    </a>\n</center>\n<Br></Br>\n<center>\n  <h1>EMERALD ITEMS!</h1>\n</center>\n\n<center><p><strong>Emerald Items!</strong> is a vanilla-friendly Forge mod that adds the <strong>childhood dream</strong> to Minecraft - <strong>Emerald Armor and Tools</strong> set.</p></center>\n<br>\n<a><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ey0fNBq.png\" title=\"LOGO\" alt=\"logo\"/></a>\n<br></br>\n<center><p>Because <strong>Emeralds are extremely rare to spawn</strong> naturally, these powerful gear pieces <strong>surpass Netherite</strong> in damage and attack speed, though for the cost of their durability, which is lower than Diamond - making them a high-risk, high-reward choice for adventurers.</p></center>\n\n<center><p>Available for <strong>Forge</strong>, <strong>NeoForge</strong> and <strong>Fabric</strong>!</p></center>\n\n***\n\nCrafting recipes follow the standard vanilla patterns for armor and tools.\n\nAs always, I recommend the [JEI](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei) mod for the recipes.\n\nEnjoy!\n\n<hr>\n<center><p>If you wish to use this in a modpack, feel free to do so!</p></center>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/tP9PZvUNjW\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/U38neWw.png\" title=\"ad_dc\" alt=\"Ad DC\" /></a>",
